# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Use a **Stack** to Solve This Problem. This Problem is Exactly **Same as Valid Parenthesis**.
# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(N)
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity:O(N)
