This problem i solved using stack.

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
The idea is to solve this problem is scan string from left to right and when string char is "a" push onto the stack and when string char is "b" then check if top of the stack is "a" or not if yes then pop "a" and push "b" if no then return false.
and if string char is "c" then check top of the stack is "b" or not if yes then pop from stack and if no then return false.
when string gets over then at the end check stack empty or not if yes then return true otherwise false;

