1. create an empty array with nums.length [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0]
1. put elements form nums[leftPartStartIndex] to all even positions of result[] and increase leftPartStartIndex to 1
1. put elements form nums[rightPartStartIndex] to all odd positions of result[] and increase rightPartStartIndex to 1
